metadata.name: Godjira Mfers #1
metadata.description: We are the final fusion! Godjira mfers by sarjira. Godjira mfers is a 1,111 unit collection that was inspired by sartoshi himself & the bad ass community at Project Godjira. This collection consists of over 69 unique hand drawn traits spanning various rarities with no two alike and 9 very special 1 of 1s. No official discord. No roadmap. But most importantly - No boundaries. Feel free to use your Godjira mfer in any way you want.
